{
  "info": {
    "name": "Pasarela BNB Bolivia",
    "description": "Colección completa para probar la pasarela de pagos QR con BNB.\n\n## Puertos (Docker Compose)\n- `9191` → API Go directa (`http://localhost:9191`) — usar aquí en Postman\n- `9292` → Frontend nginx — pantalla de pago, iFrame, integración merchant\n\n## Sin Docker (desarrollo local)\n- Cambiar `base_url` al puerto que use el Go server (ej: `http://localhost:9090`)\n\n## Variables de colección\n- `base_url` — URL base del API\n- `payment_id` — se llena automáticamente al crear un pago\n- `qr_id` — ID del QR en BNB\n- `pay_url` — URL de la pantalla de pago (para abrir en el navegador)\n\n## Flujos\n1. Crear pago → ver QR → simular webhook → verificar `paid`\n2. Crear pago → cancelar → verificar `cancelled`\n3. Abrir `pay_url` en el navegador para ver la pantalla de pago",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "pasarela-bnb-bolivia-2026"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:9191",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "URL base del API. Docker: 9191. Dev local: el puerto que uses en PORT env var."
    },
    {
      "key": "payment_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Se llena automáticamente al ejecutar cualquier 'Crear Pago'"
    },
    {
      "key": "qr_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "ID del QR en BNB — se llena automáticamente"
    },
    {
      "key": "pay_url",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "URL completa de la pantalla de pago. Abrir en el navegador o pasar a un iFrame."
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Health Check",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Servidor activo', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Status ok', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().status).to.eql('ok'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Verifica que el servidor esté corriendo."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\"status\":\"ok\"}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Pagos",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear Pago (BOB)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Respuesta tiene paymentId, qrImage y payUrl', () => {",
                  "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(j.paymentId).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "    pm.expect(j.qrId).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "    pm.expect(j.qrImage).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "    pm.expect(j.payUrl).to.be.a('string').and.include('/pay/');",
                  "    pm.expect(j.status).to.eql('pending');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Monto y moneda correctos', () => {",
                  "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(j.amount).to.eql(75);",
                  "    pm.expect(j.currency).to.eql('BOB');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('payment_id', j.paymentId);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('qr_id', j.qrId);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('pay_url', j.payUrl);",
                  "console.log('payment_id:', j.paymentId);",
                  "console.log('pay_url:', j.payUrl);",
                  "console.log('Abrir en el navegador:', j.payUrl);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"amount\": 75,\n  \"currency\": \"BOB\",\n  \"description\": \"Almuerzo Mesa 5\",\n  \"reference\": \"REST-2026-001\",\n  \"expiresAt\": \"2026-12-31\",\n  \"callbackUrl\": \"http://localhost:9292/gracias?order=REST-2026-001\"\n}",
              "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
